# Phase 15 UI Visual System

Before Phase 15 UI visual work, read `docs/prompts/CODEX_PHASE15_UI_VISUAL_REFINEMENT_SKILL.md`.

Core rules:

- Follow `docs/design/figma/**` and `docs/design/figma/optimized/**`.
- Do not freely redesign pages or use Figma PNGs as backgrounds.
- Do not create fake customer orders, fake worker tasks, fake income, fake qualifications, fake payments, fake admin metrics, or fake settlement outcomes.
- Keep all API calls same-origin; no `http://localhost:3000`, no `127.0.0.1`, no `/api/api`.
- Customer pages must preserve real catalog/pricing/order/payment-order wiring.
- Worker pages must stay honest about not-wired APIs until real worker APIs are connected.
- Admin Settlement/Governance visual work must not rewrite existing business logic or hide backend errors.
- Production remains `NO-GO` unless a separate human release instruction says otherwise.
